Entries are securely stored on Arweave,
Arweave's features are leveraged to implement metadata tagging,
GraphQL is implemented using Apollo Server to query and
retrieve existing entries. Connects with backend (Vercel
Functions) to retrieve data securely. GraphQL provides
data retrieval and facilitates content display, enabling a
data indexing and querying from Arwaeve.
Bundlr also provides trx receipt, and
